				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Loki" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>Loki is the first Play-to-Role game ever created. Play through three different card games with your friends (push-your-luck, bluffing and memory) and dive into a mystical Norse atmosphere.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;While you play, your actions and results will determine your fate as a character, and you will be able to start the fourth module, an immersive Role Playing adventure! The card games are designed to create a vibrant, thrilling and engaging atmosphere between players. Each participant will compete against the others or in team, depending on the card game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Asgard is a bluffing game where players must act as a Norse deity while bluffing to stay undercoven. The last one remaining alive wins the match.&amp;#10;Omen is a push-your-luck &amp;amp; memory game where players place bets to guess the number of cards on the board. Omen cards act as a jolly and can turn luck and memory against everybody.&amp;#10;Valhalla is a combat game where players compete against each other and against monsters to remain the last man standing in the arena.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once the games are complete, the results and the points obtained by the players, together, form the traits of their characers in Mask of Loki, the Role-playing game that acts as a forth module. The game comes with a handy game manual explaining the rules: Mask of Loki, in fact, is a very simple game (it takes half an hour to be mastered) that rewards cooperative play and awards poor luck in the previous character creation session.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hours of funny, thrilling and amazing adventures in the Norse society are waiting for you. Dive into Loki and show everybody what you are made of!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
